freebsd-sh

Standalone Meson-based extraction of the FreeBSD sh shell from chimerautils.

Build:

meson setup build
meson compile -C build

Build without libedit history and line editing:

meson setup build-noedit -Dlibedit=disabled
meson compile -C build-noedit

Run:

./build/src/sh -c 'echo ok'

Layout:

src/         shell core plus generator inputs and scripts
src/bltin/   builtin implementations (echo, kill, printf, test)
src/compat/  minimal portability shims used by this extracted tree
include/     compatibility headers copied from chimerautils

Provenance:

See UPSTREAM.md for the exact upstream commit and copied paths.
